      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior has significant paint failure, heavy rusting on the rocker panels, and a cracked windshield. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent knock and a significant oil leak, and the transmission shifts harshly between second and third gears. The interior has several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This would be best suited as a dedicated project car or a source for parts.",
